{"tid":1509340,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(營養品- 必須睇) - 白宮首席策略長兼美國總統顧問 班農 - 對香港嘅睇法","createTime":"2019-08-26T20:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:41:53.000Z","uid":232671,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a011e3a086e64f4809d147624bc6a31f6a8780","tid":1509340,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:43:45.000Z","msg":"呢段片可以話係暫時以嚟其中一段<strong>極重要</strong>、<strong>極有營養</strong>嘅片(有字幕)<br />\n有些少長, 但請大家花少少時間睇咗佢, 最少睇頭廿零分鐘 <br />\n裡面講到全球, 特別係美國對香港嘅睇法, <br />\n亦講解咗香港反送中運動點樣令全球connected一齊對抗中共<br />\n#裡面有提到香港點解咁重要, 亦有提到點解機場係春袋 (唔好問我春袋英文係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_xDQs5M7lHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_xDQs5M7lHw&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=a8b302f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_xDQs5M7lHw</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完之後大家可以諗吓下一步我哋應該點做先可以用最少傷亡換取最大成果<br />\nSir, This Way<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 香港革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c678ac96df02c1dc062ab07d986dcf94953158d","tid":1509340,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c663c01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=af6395b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=58637874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"6372b0f4449af046077303e8ad062d8391affb14","tid":1509340,"uid":175431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁即係點都要有傷亡先得喇"},{"pid":"e80b8400ef759b2faff6f9789a250501b949e411","tid":1509340,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:45:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"934c2e5872de9271155c330a4b536f08ef380016","tid":1509340,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6372b0f4449af046077303e8ad062d8391affb14","tid":1509340,"uid":175431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁即係點都要有傷亡先得喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:47:35.000Z","msg":"或者係最少付出去換取最大回報<br />\n唔一定係傷亡..."},{"pid":"42e24332691d71155abdff443dc6199549b78418","tid":1509340,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:54:06.000Z","msg":"大紀元嚟？不過可以咁訪問法都幾勁"},{"pid":"903c255021d8ae8bc5b82d99fc4515d2d2d4a63d","tid":1509340,"uid":53870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:57:47.000Z","msg":"從來革命/推翻政權<br />\n都係得2種大方向<br />\n一係流血 一係經濟<br />\n經濟就係真全港大罷工<br />\n但係大家都知香港人好鍾意番工同錢<br />\n所以我地條路得番流血<br />\n唔好諗住有外國幫我地 <br />\n我知好黑暗 亦都無人想受傷同死亡<br />\n邊個唔係靜靜地贏 但係無辦法<br />\n只好做好自己 不分化 不割席 兄弟各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n今日新疆 明日香港<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"90d5e5074f0608fdc6c10c2659869e67390b0b7c","tid":1509340,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"應該係前顧問<br />\n冇記錯<br />\n佢比人炒咗？"},{"pid":"bc8a0f7d2d7bdd0b70b360cbade36b4c5e816b00","tid":1509340,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:04:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0ffcad6562b7c702f052d7e8666d249c850f4cc","tid":1509340,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b59e462f54fc47c184b5066fa98fcf8ec32d9db","tid":1509340,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:13:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c5c2e9e962923199c3ad28c3c790b4e23a1aeebd","tid":1509340,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:47:46.000Z","msg":"p牌仔，幫唔倒推，但真係好值得睇"},{"pid":"3c1c7ac2636883bcff4963cc18b14f4c88735d0a","tid":1509340,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d5e5074f0608fdc6c10c2659869e67390b0b7c","tid":1509340,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"應該係前顧問<br />\n冇記錯<br />\n佢比人炒咗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:49:37.000Z","msg":"係前<br />\n<br />\n不過「炒咗」<br />\n做嘢更加無束縛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a12143bf23a817b2af976dd4ce04421922d428","tid":1509340,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"412727bbe9915751f1d4465a1c2e55af7533a73e","tid":1509340,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"142d132b796f0b805112b5064876c2f48aff84b4","tid"